@node "Distribution" "Distribution        "

 @{b}Distribution@{ub}

 Basically,  the  evaluation  version  of  FileQuest   may   be   freely
 distributed as long as the following conditions are met:

 The distributor may only charge a fee up to the costs  of  obtaining  a
 public  domain diskette from Fred Fish. The distributor agrees to cease
 distributing the programs and data involved if requested to  do  so  by
 the  author.  The distributor may only distribute an unmodified copy of
 the original program, with all the supplied documentation and copyright
 notices left intact.

 For more details, see the @{"License" link "Licence" 0} section.
@endnode

